################################################################################
# RESTFX-DDD PROJECT — .gitignore
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# PURPOSE:
#   Defines which files and directories should not be committed to Git.
#   Maintains repository cleanliness and avoids polluting history with
#   build artifacts, caches, IDE configs, or temporary files.
#
# GUIDING PRINCIPLES:
#   • Everything generated → ignored.
#   • Everything source or config → kept.
#   • Mirrors Docker ignore list for consistency.
#
# COMMON CATEGORIES:
#   - Build outputs: binaries, coverage, dist, cache
#   - Local configs: .env, *.local.yaml
#   - IDE metadata: .vscode/, .idea/
#   - Code generation: buf/sqlc/oapi outputs
#   - CI & Terraform state: .terraform/, *.tfstate
#
# MAINTENANCE:
#   • Update this file whenever a new build artifact folder is introduced.
#   • Do not ignore /config or /pkg sources unless explicitly local.
#   • Ensure CI-generated artifacts (coverage.html, reports) are excluded.
################################################################################

